title: 5.11 Tactical Men's Defender-Flex Regular Fit Jeans, 7 Pockets, Fitted Waistband, Style 74477, New Finish
description: Regular Fit for Classic Comfort – Provides a relaxed yet structured feel for all-day wear.
7 Versatile Pockets for Essential Storage – Designed for easy access and functionality on the go.
Durable Double-Needle Construction with Bar Tacks – Reinforced at high-stress areas for long-lasting strength.
Rivet Reinforcements at Hand & Coin Pockets – Adds extra durability to withstand daily wear and tear.
76% cotton/ 24% polyester with Lycra T400 Tough Max mechanical stretch denim,10-oz.

Whether it's a weekend in the backcountry or a night out on the town, the Defender-Flex Jean rolls with you. An innovative cotton/polyester (Lycra T400 Tough Max) mechanical stretch denim means better stretch and recovery. Five pocket styling plus two mag pockets up your tactical game. Imported. Also available in Slim Fit and Straight Fit
